      <title>中国财富基金誓言在稳定市场中发挥作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/china-s-wealth-fund-vows-to-play-role-in-stabilizing-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国1.24万亿美元的主权财富基金誓言将在2024年帮助缓解风险和稳定市场，这是国有企业在提振中国陷入困境的股市方面发挥更大作用的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/china-s-wealth-fund-vows-to-play-role-in-stabilizing-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 02:42:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国国债收益率上升，美元升至12月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/dollar-climbs-toward-highest-since-december-as-us-yields-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国国债收益率攀升，而投资者寻求有关美国降息时机的更多线索，美元指数升至一个月高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/dollar-climbs-toward-highest-since-december-as-us-yields-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 02:09:04 GMT</pubDate>
